Large Group Quote Lightning Web Component

The Large Group Quote LWC is designed to help you build complex quotes. It features a side panel for editing line items and buttons for common actions, such as issuing policies and comparing quote version histories.

This component supports multi-root quotes and synchronous and asynchronous rating for large group quoting. For small and medium group quoting, use the insQuote LWC.
